Package: sstvars
Type: Package
Title: Toolkit for Structural Smooth Transition Vector Autoregressive Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Savi", "Virolainen", email = "savi.virolainen@helsinki.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5075-6821"))
Maintainer: Savi Virolainen <savi.virolainen@helsinki.fi>
Description: Toolkit for reduced form and structural smooth transition vector autoregressive
  models and threshold vector autoregressive models. Maximum likelihood estimation of models with
  various types of transition weight functions and Gaussian or Student's t conditional distribution. Constrained
  estimation employing various types of constraints is available. Several identification methods for identifying
  the structural models are included.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
URL: https://github.com/saviviro/sstvars
BugReports: https://github.com/saviviro/sstvars/issues
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
